faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n第7季都唔係,其實應該要完<br />\n但佢話續我都會想繼續睇<br />\n唉,又唔知點樣闖禍啦佢地"},{"pid":"18c11eee6273bbca2e04866db3d69471d5e84a20","tid":377482,"uid":103380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T18:54:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>得第一季好笑<br />\n成家有合作</blockquote><br />\n季季都有啲位成家合作架<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8a1a81771154c887cb9b75cc575106c69acfbbb","tid":377482,"uid":103380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T18:56:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想開好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n身邊冇人睇 見之前有連登仔睇<br />\n睇下開個post 有冇人入黎討論<br />\n<br />\n我已經擺shameless喺我favourite list No.1<br />\n其次係GOT <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n估唔到會有人開,shameless係我最愛既美劇</blockquote><br />\n之前有啲美劇post都有講過<br />\n見好少連登仔有睇 都有既<br />\n所以睇下開個post專講會唔會有多啲人討論<br />\n<br />\n又想引多啲人追<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可以簡介下,介紹下人物,不過成7季,細節我都唔太記得.<br />\n<br />\n總之劇情就係 解決問題-&gt;闖禍-&gt;再解決-&gt;再闖禍 loop</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我重睇左兩次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個簡介你都講左<br />\n就係窮人既家庭既生活<br />\n<br />\n不過每次季尾又梗係要sad ending <br />\n<br />\nFiona結婚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n第7季都唔係,其實應該要完<br />\n但佢話續我都會想繼續睇<br />\n唉,又唔知點樣闖禍啦佢地</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係睇住Debbie對波大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfd6a79b944f7b69cfbd2cc2a0d10e4a5e28c4b4","tid":377482,"uid":126247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T18:57:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>得第一季好笑<br />\n成家有合作</blockquote><br />\n季季都有啲位成家合作架<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講起合作....一早要踢走frank啦,忍咁耐<br />\n不過上面講得無錯,前面有mickey,sheila,mandy,karen呢D<br />\n真係好睇D,不過我覺得7季都好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"726915a6f23719ceeb2938faec4a238c9ad7b895","tid":377482,"uid":13984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T19:02:40.000Z","msg":"Season 8要等到11月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8745494a17b30113750fb4e478ab97b0bb1457a7","tid":377482,"uid":14407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T19:06:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>開頭幾季真係幾好<br />\n苦中帶甜<br />\n完全呈現到個種物質一無所有都可以生活燦爛嘅氛圍<br />\n<br />\n到大籮柚走咗<br />\n然後比Mickey 條線帶到故事高峰<br />\n之後已經寫唔返個種感覺<br />\n<br />\n特別講大哥酗酒連續十幾集個條線<br />\n令到套劇真係悶咗</blockquote><br />\n大蘿柚係邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就算Ian轉左幾多條仔 我都係覺得佢同Micky先係一對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n反而lip酗酒個到唔差<br />\n唔知點講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nsteve jimmy 闖入大家姐同佢地一家人嘅生活圈子，係同老豆一樣推動到成套劇<br />\n前者令到大家覺得仆街極都有個正常人喺側邊<br />\n老豆就展現出低處未算低個種底線<br />\n<br />\n好多時都係佢2個加埋Kevin V 去carry 成家人，令到個故事有種好奇妙嘅張力，令人覺得「生活應該係咁」<br />\n<br />\n所以到大籮柚steve 唔做之後，mickey mandy 埋尾，個劇寫唔返個種「正常生活」，一味慘同虐，係好touching ，但唔夠日常<br />\n<br />\n最終要開主線，分工晒大家個套路發展，好似ian 病 lip 酒 deb 反叛 carl 正義感<br />\n<br />\n但要靠主線發揮，就唔夠功力了，好似Deb 同大哥好明顯已經係寫壞咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：頭4季睇咗四五次，係最愛嘅美劇"},{"pid":"7b012827ff609058947eeae256682561de43c2ff","tid":377482,"uid":14407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T19:09:43.000Z","msg":"唔好意思有少少劇透<br />\n但唔影響大家睇的，無特別穿橋位"},{"pid":"b15